'''Gold Ore''' is a [[:Category:Resources|resource]] obtained largely from [[Mining#Mining Nodes|Gold Nodes]] with a [[Pickaxes|Pickaxe]].

==Locations==
* [[Mining#Mining Nodes|Gold nodes]] in [[The Mines|the Mines]] at levels 80+
* Gold Nodes in the [[Skull Cavern|Skull Cavern]] rarely at levels 60+ and more commonly at levels 80+
* Nodes can spawn in the [[Quarry]] or in the quarry on the [[Farm Maps|Hill-top and Four-Corners Farm Maps]]
* Breaking boxes and barrels in the mines.
* [[Ghost]]s have a 20% chance of dropping 1-3 gold ore.
* [[Fishing#Treasure Chests|Fishing treasure chests]]
* Beachfront [[Artifact Spot]]s
* [[Frozen Geode]]s, [[Magma Geode]]s, or [[Omni Geode]]s
* [[Copper Pan|Panning]]
* [[Traveling Cart]] for {{tprice|25}}
* [[Blacksmith]] for {{price|400}} each in year 1, {{price|750}} each in year 2+.
* [[Lava Eel]] [[Fish Pond]] when population reaches 3 or more

==Smelting==
Gold ore can be smelted in a [[Furnace]] to create a [[Gold Bar]]. The smelting requires 5 gold ore and 1 [[coal]] to begin and takes approximately 5 in-game hours to complete.

